item.title: TaeKwonDo Inauguration Huge Success
item.author: LiYan Chow,
item.description: The work from countless months of planning, organisation and training finally came together as Imperial College Union TaeKwonDo (ICUTKD) hosted their very own competition at the Ethos sports hall last Sunday.
